OL,3,CMan stole #28k worth of cereal and
OL,4,Csaid he had given it to foodbank
OL,6,FA delivery driver who stole a large
OL,7,Fshipment of cereal, then lied about
OL,8,Fdonating it to a foodbank, has been
OL,9,Fconvicted.
OL,11,FClifford Wyatt, 43, of Lund Avenue in
OL,12,FRadcliffe, had been working at
OL,13,FBramhall Transport in Warrington for
OL,14,Fjust six days when he entered the
OL,15,Fcompany's site in October last year
OL,16,Fand took a tractor.
