OL,3,CMan stole #28k worth of cereal and
OL,4,Csaid he had given it to foodbank
OL,6,FDriving the unit to the nearby MAXI
OL,7,FHaulage depot, he loaded up a large
OL,8,Ftrailer containing #28,163 worth of
OL,9,FWheat Bisk cereal and drove nearly 30
OL,10,Fmiles to Meadow Self Storage in
OL,11,FFailsworth, Manchester, where an
OL,12,Fassociate was waiting to help him
OL,13,Funload his haul.
OL,15,FLiverpool Crown Court heard that Wyatt
OL,16,Fstole a total 792 containers each
OL,17,Fcontaining 22 boxes of Wheat Bisk,
OL,18,Fwhich is often stocked in Aldi.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
