OL,3,CMan stole #28k worth of cereal and
OL,4,Csaid he had given it to foodbank
OL,6,FAfter unloading the pallets, he
OL,7,Freturned the trailer and tractor to
OL,8,FWarrington, where the missing shipment
OL,9,Fwas quickly discovered.
OL,11,FProsecutor Joanne Daniels, at
OL,12,FLiverpool Crown Court said: "Bramhall
OL,13,FTransport manager Thomas Jones, having
OL,14,Fchecked the CCTV, rang Wyatt for an
OL,15,Fexplanation. The defendant admitted
OL,16,Ftaking the tractor... He claimed he
OL,17,Fhad taken it to a foodbank in Oldham
OL,18,Fas it was damaged stock, and claimed
OL,19,Fthe yard manager had given him
OL,20,Fpermission to go."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
