OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F398A1731583181
OL,3,CMan stole #28k worth of cereal and
OL,4,Csaid he had given it to foodbank
OL,6,FHowever, the yard manager said no such
OL,7,Finteraction had occurred.
OL,9,FMs Daniels said: "Enquiries were made
OL,10,Fto Oldham foodbank and it was found
OL,11,Fthe foodbank is actually closed on
OL,12,FSundays, and they only accept small
OL,13,Fdonations. They could not accept large
OL,14,Fdonations from HGVs, and didn't
OL,15,Freceive any Wheat Bisks on October 8."
OL,17,FThe court heard Wyatt had attended the
OL,18,Ffoodbank on 9 October and attempted to
OL,19,Fobtain a receipt saying he had donated
OL,20,Fthe boxes of cereal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
