OL,6,FOn 18 October, the manager of Bramhall
OL,7,FTransport attended Meadow Self Storage
OL,8,Fand retrieved the majority of the
OL,9,FWheat Bisks, which had been stored in
OL,10,Fsix lockers.
OL,12,FWyatt, who has three past convictions
OL,13,Ffor four offences including theft,
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to taking a vehicle
OL,15,Fwithout consent, and theft.
