OL,6,FIn his defence Olivia Beesley said:
OL,7,F"While he does have previous
OL,8,Fconvictions they are limited. He has
OL,9,Fnot offended in 20 years prior to
OL,10,Fthis. There's a realistic
OL,11,Frehabilitation prospect and he has
OL,12,Fshown he can, and has, lived a law
OL,13,Fabiding life.
