OL,6,FSentencing, judge David Potter said:
OL,7,F"There was significant planning in the
OL,8,Ftime you chose to commit the theft,
OL,9,Fpreparing the storage containers ready
OL,10,Fto receive the stolen goods, and
OL,11,Fattempt to hide your criminal
OL,12,Factivities. It's aggravated by your
OL,13,Fattempt to place blame on others.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
